Yeah, but that
damage is only 200

00:13:35.248 --> 00:13:37.251
and my Gate of Fire
will block anything

00:13:37.284 --> 00:13:38.785
that's less than 300.

00:13:38.819 --> 00:13:41.155
Yeah, but Sweet
Guitar's special ability

00:13:41.222 --> 00:13:43.890
can double the damage
that my Divaridis deals.

00:13:46.960 --> 00:13:48.461
Oh no.

00:13:48.495 --> 00:13:50.564
The last time I checked no
matter how you do the math,

00:13:50.598 --> 00:13:52.566
400 is still greater than 300.

00:13:57.070 --> 00:13:59.639
Then my Sweet Guitar
gains attack points equal

00:13:59.706 --> 00:14:04.445
to the damage I just dealt
raising her from 2200 to 2600.

