Next, by banishing Trickstar
Fusion from my graveyard,

00:14:07.981 --> 00:14:10.384
I'm then allowed to retrieve
a different Trickstar

00:14:10.451 --> 00:14:12.719
and then add it to my
hand but I'm not allowed

00:14:12.786 --> 00:14:14.654
to summon that
monster this turn,

00:14:14.688 --> 00:14:16.790
but I think Trickstar
Calobane would rather hang

00:14:16.824 --> 00:14:18.558
with me than sleep in the grave.

00:14:19.860 --> 00:14:21.996
It's time to bring
this duel to an end.

00:14:22.029 --> 00:14:23.463
Here goes.

